vptestmd sign_mask, t, SIGN_BIT    // sign_mask[i] = (t[i] >> 31) & 1, tests bit 31
vpaddd{sign_mask} t, t, P
```

`vptestmd` runs on port 5! And we avoid reading `x_1` again (which was needed for the comparison `vpcmpltud k, x_1, x_2_twiddle`).

